{{Top|real|title=''Star Wars'': Blogs}}
'''''Star Wars: Blogs''''' was a section of the official ''[[Star Wars]]'' website, allowing fans, authors, actors and other people to write their own [[Wikipedia:Blog|blog]].

It was superseded by one central blog named [[Star Wars Blog|''Star Wars'' Blog]].

